<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8"></meta>
    <title>STEP4</title>

    <!--Angular Setting-->
    <script src="/angular/angular.js"></script>
    <script src="/chart.js/dist/Chart.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/angular-chart.js/dist/angular-chart.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/angular-resource/angular-resource.min.js"></script>

    <!--Boot Strap-->
    <script src="/jquery-1.12.0/jquery1.12.0.min.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/bootstrap/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <script src="/bootstrap/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>

    <script src="/graph/js/module.js"></script>
    <script src="/graph/js/graph1.js"></script>
    <script src="/graph/js/graph2.js"></script>
    <script src="/graph/js/graph3.js"></script>
</head>

<body ng-app="app">

<div>
    <% include headbar.ejs%>
</div>

<div class="container">
    <div class="col">
        <div class="panel panel-default col-lg-6 col-sm-12 ng-scope" ng-controller="BarCtrl">
            <h1>GRAPH 1 : 연도별 일의 수</h1>
            <canvas id="bar" class="chart chart-bar" chart-data="data" chart-labels="labels" chart-series="series">
            </canvas>
        </div>
    </div>


    <div class="col">
        <div class="panel panel-default col-lg-6 col-sm-12 ng-scope" ng-controller="RadarCtrl">
            <h1>GRAPH 2 : 부서간 심의결과 비교</h1>
            <select name="singleSelect" ng-model="graph0" ng-change="request_query(graph0, 0)">
                <option ng-repeat="department in department_list" value="{{department}}">{{department}}</option>
            </select>
            <select name="singleSelect" ng-model="graph1" ng-change="request_query(graph1, 1)">
                <option ng-repeat="department in department_list" value="{{department}}">{{department}}</option>
            </select>
            <br>
            <canvas id="radar" class="chart chart-radar" chart-data="data" chart-options="options" chart-labels="labels" chart-dataset-override="datasetOverride">
            </canvas>
            <p>데이터가 작은부서는 작게 보일 수 있습니다.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="panel panel-default col-lg-6 col-sm-12 ng-scope" ng-controller="DoughnutCtrl">
            <h1>GRAPH 3 : 각 부서의 일의 수</h1>
            <canvas id="doughnut" class="chart chart-doughnut" chart-data="data" chart-labels="labels">
            </canvas>
        </div>
    </div>

</div>

</body>


</html>

